    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[I]n nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/355" key="#Princeps">Radelgarius</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3638" key="#Intercessory #Principissa"
                            >Tasselgarde</persName> dilecte coniugis nostre, tibi <persName
                            key="#Gold #Specialized_workers" ref="#people/3633">Autulo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gold #Specialized_workers">aurifici</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >rem illam</rs> in <placeName ref="#places/3467"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Bitoranu</placeName> et in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Cursanum in finibus
                            Folianensis</placeName> que fuit de <rs key="#Slave">servis</rs> sacris
                        nostri <rs key="#Palatium">palatii</rs>, quam <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi
                            homines</rs> per annos viginti <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">sine preceptum
                            tenunt</rs>, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum preceptum predictam rem tu et heredes tui habere et
                        possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus,
                        gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed
                        perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex
                        iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            ref="#people/3637">Benedictus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName> primo anno, mense novembrio,
                        quarta decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
